title: [Blighted Forest, Treetop]
description: The elaborate maze of tree trails ends to the east and there, breaks in the forest reveal the startling yellow-gold color of a meadow below.  To the other directions, the wide avenues crossing thick, intersecting tree boughs stretch away into the leafy greenish half-light.

The elaborate maze of tree trails ends to the east and there, breaks in the forest reveal the silvery hue of a moonlit meadow below.  To the other directions, the wide avenues crossing thick, intersecting tree boughs stretch away into the leafy shadows.
